Specimen Requirements:
Container/Tube: Plastic, 60-mL urine bottle
Specimen Volume: 15 mL
Collection Instructions: 
1. Collect a first-morning, random urine collection.
2. Patient should collect specimen prior to eating foods rich in vitamin C or taking vitamin C supplements.
Additional Information: Indicate patient's age and sex.
Reject Due To:
Hemolysis	NA
Thawing	Warm reject; Cold OK
Lipemia	NA
Icterus	NA
Other	NA
